Translate (Material stage keyword)
==================================

Description
-----------

The **translate** keyword translates a stage by the given offset.

Usage
-----

`translate [x], [y]`

Parameters
----------

-   [x] = The x offset
-   [y] = The y offset

Example
-------

Scroll a stage at a constant rate

`{`
`   translate  time, time`
`   map     textures/custom/foo.tga`
`}`

Notes
-----

The [Scroll\_(Material\_stage\_keyword).html scroll] keyword is an alias for this keyword.


